title: Captain Marvel: Gemma Chan annuncia la sua partecipazione ai reshoot
body:
Captain Marvel: Gemma Chan annuncia la sua partecipazione ai reshoot

Captain Marvel è nel bel mezzo delle riprese aggiuntive e tra coloro che sono tornati sul set c’è anche l’attrice Gemma Chan che veste i panni di Minn-Erva.

I fan dell’Universo Cinematografico Marvel devono ancora aspettare sei mesi per Avengers 4, ma in realtà non c’è questo grande problema, visto che l’attesa verrà smorzata dal film con protagonista Brie Larson, che interpreta la potente…

Cats a pretty cool. There were a lot of stray cats in some of the buildings I used to live in. Some of them were kinda mean, but I think they were just hungry like I was.

Yeah I like waffles!!!!

Jurassic Park! Dinosaurs are super cool!

VARIANT COVER BY RON LIM
HERO FOR A DAY, HERO FOR A PLANET!

caption:
CAPTAIN MARVEL #2

KELLY THOMPSON (W) • CARMEN CARNERO (A)
Cover by Amanda Conner & Paul Mounts
Variant Cover by CHRIS BACHALO
WRAPAROUND Design Variant Cover by CARMEN CARNERO
Movie Variant Cover Also Available
REVOLUTION!
The classic Fantastic Four villain MAHKIZMO has taken over Manhattan’s Roosevelt Island and turned it into an apocalyptic wasteland! When CAPTAIN MARVEL ends up trapped there and cut off from the rest of world (including any Avengers-shaped reinforcements!), she’ll need to build her own team out of allies, old and new — SPIDER-WOMAN, HAZMAT, ECHO and a man known only as SOM — in order to start a revolution to free the island’s civilian inhabitants. With that kind of backup, Mahkizmo should be toast — but not everything is what it seems on this island…
32 PGS./Rated T+ …$3.99
